reviews.text:
I really nice Ice Cream Vape Not to much Lemon, exatly right after 3 days, best after 7days. &#xD;
Longer steeping mutes the Lemon. I  decreased the sweetener to 0.8%, That helps against the Lemon muting, because there is Etyl Malthol in the TPA Sweetener.. If that is not sweet enough, its better to use CAPs Super Sweet, because there is no EM inside.&#xD;
&#xD;
Thanks for this great recipe.
